# The workspace — a data engineer's daily surfaces

- **Notebooks** — write PySpark / SQL, attach to compute, run
- **Git folders** & the file tree — code under version control
- **Catalog Explorer** — browse Unity Catalog: catalogs, schemas, tables, volumes, lineage
- **SQL editor, Lakeflow Jobs & pipelines**, the Compute page
- **Account > workspaces** — the UC metastore is account-level, shared across workspaces
